    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007290/extras/0048dfa5f934840569ce16c6eedf8d2c.avif?t=1748928447\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007290/extras_big/0048dfa5f934840569ce16c6eedf8d2c.avif?t=1748928447 width=800 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smol Survivors is a 2D reverse bullet-heck where smol blocks have become lost and need to find their friends and a way back home while fighting through hordes of enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007290/extras/4fbd6c45ffeb4a5e6f8167d2f3fb561f.poster.avif?t=1748928447\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007290/extras/4fbd6c45ffeb4a5e6f8167d2f3fb561f.webm?t=1748928447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007290/extras/4fbd6c45ffeb4a5e6f8167d2f3fb561f.mp4?t=1748928447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 minute runs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 10 smol survivors to rescue</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapons from fireballs to cheese boomerangs to trash zombies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quests to earn some extra currency and help find lost survivors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overpowered abilities and super weapons that may or may not break the game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cosmetic gacha shop </p></li></ul>",
